When you are doing assasinations on the planet surface, the best tactic
is to take off about 30 mins before the ship is about to turn up.
Instead of boosting out of the atmosphere, just fly your ship a little
way out of the starport, and rough land with your ship facing the
launch-pad.  Switch on text, and then time-skip to about a minute
before your target is about to take off.  Sure enough, your target
will appear, and you can lock onto him, engage autopilot and start
blasting.

