> contract from some 30 mins before I need to be there until several days
> after. The person never appears please help cause its getting annoying.

If you've waited for several days, I would guess that you are using time
accelleration.  Don't!

I have used this technique and the target has never failed to arrive.

1.  Leave the target base 6-9 hours before the due time.
2.  Time accellerate until you are within 2 minutes of the correct time.
3.  Set time to real time.
4.  The target will leave exactly when your contract says.

If you are time speeding, you will never see the victim leave.


