    - Autopilot + max compression to arrive to "vicinity of planet"
    - 3-4 compression and 50 000 km/h, fly to 7000-8000 km distance
    - Orbit the planet (outside view for easier target searching)
    - Lock on target when it is in horizon
    - 10 000 km/h and 2-3 compression until distance is 500 km
    - Approach in 30 000 m altitude, accelerating to 40 000 km and 
      fly over the base, I usually take photos and engage hyperdrive 
      before enemies can fire at me.

